The main features that are used in this paper for system- level design studies are summarized here and will be explained in detail in the following sections:
 Task
o Location of threats
o Areas with high probability of harboring threats o Difficulty of classifying threats
 UAV
o Flight performance constraints o Navigation autonomy levels
o Camera image quality
 Operator
o Inherent skill
o Dynamic effects of workload, fatigue, and situational awareness
 Human-agent interaction o Level of automation o Interaction time
